      <div class="field-group" style="flex:0.8"><label>Price (£/m)</label><input type="number" class="wire-price" step="0.01" min="0" value="0.10" title="Wire price £/m. 0.5mm²: £0.10, 1.5mm²: £0.18, 4mm²: £0.40"/></div>
